Invocation Name: quick workout
des:
Now, Alexa can help you to do your quick workout. No need phone or any sound system to play music for your daily quick workouts. Alexa will do that for you.

To start, just say,
Alexa, start quick workout
and it will start your 7-minute quick workout.

For more help regarding any issue/feedback, write us at alexa@hauper.com

Thanks!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
